The paper deals with designing a compressed index for efficiently computing and querying overlaps between pairs of words in a given set. This problem is relevant in various areas of computer science, including text algorithms (cs.DS), information retrieval (cs.IR), computational complexity (cs.CC), data mining (cs.DM), and machine learning (cs.LG). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
